{"tid":1096997,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貨車翻側啤酒落一地 墨西哥上百居民當場瘋狂暢飲","createTime":"2019-04-08T06:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T07:35:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c889030bc10cd9c2e3ec8b0cbbbe5e029267a1bc","tid":1096997,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:01:12.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】墨西哥上周三（3日）發生大貨車翻側意外，一整車的啤酒全都灑落在地，引來上百名附近居民狂搶啤酒，甚至不少人當場暢飲起來。<br />\n意外發生在墨西哥坎佩切州（Campeche）的高速公路上，從現場畫面中可以看到，一大群人聚集在傾覆的貨車周圍挑揀沒有損壞的啤酒，事故一發生，有「免費啤酒」喝的消息迅速傳開，居民們呼朋引伴叫人來一起搬啤酒。有的人一整箱地搬，有人則當場打開暢飲。墨西哥警方抵達現場時，雖然拉起了封鎖線，但也沒有阻止這些居民，目前也沒有任何人遭逮捕。<br />\n據墨西哥當地媒體報道，現場聚集了超過100人，甚至還有小孩跟著爸媽一起來搬啤酒，人群不僅把啤酒一掃而空，最後甚至連貨車的輪胎都被偷走。<br />\n但當地居民對於這樣的行為卻不以為然，他們表示：「別擔心，啤酒廠都為這些貨物投過保，不會有任何損失的。」但還是引來許多墨西哥網民批評，表示這樣行為根本是犯法的，尤其竟然讓未成年的孩子參與其中。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190408/_2019040812592770547.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190408%2F_2019040812592770547.jpg&h=4245057a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190408/_2019040812592889058.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190408%2F_2019040812592889058.jpg&h=449ebc10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1474767/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1474767%2F&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUTWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=1703e4f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1474767%2F&h=8c46872c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1474767/</a>"},{"pid":"331e5a2c5a1cee0f5f0f25538d606c59a80e8d18","tid":1096997,"uid":82450,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:03:54.000Z","msg":"但當地居民對於這樣的行為卻不以為然，他們表示：「<span style=\"color: red;\">別擔心，啤酒廠都為這些貨物投過保，不會有任何損失的。</span>」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262a2733bb569d899105d79c77c5e107ac03f9cf","tid":1096997,"uid":18241,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:05:44.000Z","msg":"支國人：墨西哥人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672c9cf854e59a72724ea59128c0034537110a73","tid":1096997,"uid":7323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"瘋狂暢飲啤酒，痛快暢飲啤酒。"},{"pid":"5fa6b9cbaacf1aac6fef81b4261769fda64a34d5","tid":1096997,"uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:09:23.000Z","msg":"人群不僅把啤酒一掃而空，最後甚至連貨車的輪胎都被偷走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1f72cdaa1d3f4be4226872388270d746871a3a","tid":1096997,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fa6b9cbaacf1aac6fef81b4261769fda64a34d5","tid":1096997,"uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:09:23.000Z","msg":"人群不僅把啤酒一掃而空，最後甚至連貨車的輪胎都被偷走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"跣過車嘅軚"},{"pid":"5db1b86e1d7623b32024cf00f8853b4bf70301d3","tid":1096997,"uid":43983,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:15:27.000Z","msg":"諗起之前有單中東人偷油車油<br />\n點知點著左爆炸死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52cde1782208af55cb1332748ca72dc66e6ae63","tid":1096997,"uid":107927,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:15:44.000Z","msg":"唔怪得美國想起圍牆"},{"pid":"7973405f981762f3f9f24c29b8d35f8a8442a2f4","tid":1096997,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5db1b86e1d7623b32024cf00f8853b4bf70301d3","tid":1096997,"uid":43983,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:15:27.000Z","msg":"諗起之前有單中東人偷油車油<br />\n點知點著左爆炸死哂<img src